text:
Townsville Crocodiles vs Melbourne United Tips, Odds and Betting – 2015 NBL Round 1 Posted by Jozef Dobrovic + on 09/10/2015 at 10:27 am 
Friday (09/10/2015) 2015 NBL Round 1 game is between Townsville Crocodiles and Melbourne United. We take a look at both teams odds and give our tips and value tips for the match.
